Fleurons Cafetière 

The bridge between what we were and what we will be in the coming years, we present to you our first offline outlet, our first cafetière.

While you sip your freshly brewed coffee, you can take Pinterest-y pictures in almost each and every corner of our cafe. Don’t forget to notice the details, after all, our heart’s in there 🤍

We can’t wait to see you at the cafe now! 🤍

📍 Rajouri Garden, Next to gate number 8, Rajouri Garden metro station

latestPosts.caption:
Cocomelon Hampers!

We curated the cutest cocomelon theme hampers this weekend! These 100% Eggless hampers were presented in a custom pink tray, and covered with a neon green net (you can customise too!) and contained: 
• Ombre Center-Filled Chocolates 
• Triple Chocolate Cookies 
• Rainbow Cookies
• Almond Praline Cake 
• Blueberry Cake Jar
• Tiramisu Brownie
• Rainbow Brownie 

These were accompanied with a Thankyou Card and Menu for the hampers. Not to forget, the super cute coco-melon cut-outs that decorated the entire hamper!! 

You can get your hampers customised also! Fleurons is 100% Eggless! We have over 40 options to choose from!

Lunchbox Cakes Aesthetics 
.
With these 300g Bento/Lunchbox Cakes being all the rage right now and for the right reasons, it only make sense to indulge in more than just one! And sometimes, you might wanna treat someone with 5 of these! 💫
.
You can choose different flavours/colour/text options for your bento cakes. And what could be better than a range of aesthetic pastel shades. 
.
Original Flavours: Belgian Chocolate, Nutella Milk Chocolate Truffle, Classic Chocolate Truffle, Vanilla Blueberry, Vanilla Pineapple. 
.

this dreamy floral café serves up ceremonial-grade matcha that’s as photogenic as it is pure.
